name: Ideate Design - Covid 19 App
description:
Subscribe Youtube for support : Click here

Hello Everyone,

Today we will see how to create UI Design for #Covid-19 App. By using the app we can learn about covid19 tips, we can register for #vaccine & corona test also we can see our nearby covid specialized hospital with their available general bed, ICU bed, and ambulance number. this app also allows us to book a seat or call for an emergency ambulance. Hope everyone will love the concept.
